title: 이달의소녀탐구 #73 (LOONA TV #73)
summary:
The girls are going to have dinner right now.
0:04 -- YeoJin is very talkative and HyunJin is sharing an umbrella with her. YeoJin talks a
lot and HyunJin: “Jo-yong-hi hae! (Be quiet!)”.
0:14 -- YeoJin makes a meme-able angry face.
0:16 -- HyunJin: “Oh my god~!”. YeoJin: “Kiseuneun Daeume!” (HyunJin regrets sharing
an umbrella with her. Or does she? 🤔🤔🤔🤔)
0:23 -- 2Jin sing HyunJin’s “Around You”. YeoJin asks whether HeeJin recorded a part of
the song. HyunJin tells her that it she sang the harmony as well.
0:37 -- HyunJin: "😉" (What a troll!)
0:42 -- YeoJin suspects they are all trying to fool her. HyunJin: “Be quiet if you know!”
0:48 -- HyunJin: “Jo-yong!”. YeoJin imitates her.
